Package it.uniroma3.mat.extendedset

Interface Summary
ExtendedSet<T> A SortedSet with fast intersection/union/difference and other set operations.
ExtendedSet.ExtendedIterator<X> Extended version of the Iterator interface
 

Class Summary
AbstractExtendedSet<T> An implementation of SortedSet with fast intersection/union/difference and other set operations.
ArrayMap<T> A Map backed by an array, where keys are the indices of the array, and values are the elements of the array.
ConciseSet This is CONCISE: COmpressed 'N' Composable Integer Set.
ExtendedSet.ExtendedSetComparator<X> Compare sets according to their lexicographical order.
ExtendedSet.Statistics Statistical data.
FastSet An AbstractExtendedSet implementation based on BitSet
IndexedSet<T> An AbstractExtendedSet implementation that maps elements to an integer set referred to as "indices".
